",1438673.90003055,905932.5078170703,"Nice little stream with good flow and abundant small gravel’s upstream. May be crossings downstream on private land. column1: 2023-10-05T12:14:12Z,,22200081,,,,22200081,,1468680,385,Crooked Creek ,Loseth Road ,,MOTI,Closed Bottom Structure,Oval Culvert,,2.8,13, Two pipes at 1.4 m diameter each. Crossing is only 5 m downstream of the railway crossing. Stream has far more volume of water at this location than it did below Highway 5.
